  "body": "I want to be able to have a flag to toggle listening to bls topic.\n\nThis can be a develop only flag, I don't expect to need to use it but it'll be potentially handy in some flood scenarios, or scenarios where a larger provider wants to prioritise only their changes in their blocks.\n\nI was thinking something like\n`--Xbls_to_execution_channel_enabled=true` as default\n\nThe wrinkle will be if we need to subscribe to send messages, which i expect that we probably do.",
